snippet.title: Chains of Fury - Official Kickstarter Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Take another look at gameplay and more in this brutal trailer for the first-person retro looter-shooter game, Chains of Fury.

A Kickstarter campaign for Chains of Fury is available now. Chains of Fury aims to release on PC first, and later for Nintendo Switch, PlayStation, and Xbox. A demo for the game is also available today, November 9, on Steam.

Learn more about the Kickstarter campaign here: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/gamingfactory/chains-of-fury

#IGN #Gaming
